    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, \"toxic nationalism\"? that seems a bit harsh. what about people who say you need a shared sense of identity or patriotism just so people actually care about their neighbors and follow the same rules? isn't that necessary for a society to actually function? or are you saying that's also a bad thing?",
